<p>(责编：董兆瑞、高星) </p>
➜广西人异地就医，医保咋报销？攻略来了
http://www.sohu.com/a/414363154_114731	9397
<p style="text-align: center;"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20200822/1d33a8d785114e61a980ee1fba6b6d50.png" width="600" height="2664" /></p>
